Starplot-gliese provides data files from the NASA Astronomical Data Center on 
a catalogue of nearby stars.
<<
DescPackaging: <<
Patch adds 'DESTDIR' to Makefile and modifies 'DATADIR', and also modifies 
install target to install files in correct directory.
PatchScript moves INSTALL file to INSTALL.txt to avoid 'make install: up to 
date' error when installing.
InstallScript creates necessary directories not created by installation.
<<
